text: Bullvalene is a hydrocarbon. It has a chemical formula of C10H10. It is a type of molecule with no permanent structure. Compounds that share the molecular formula, include: * Basketene * Cyclodecapentaene * Dialin * Divinylbenzene * Diisopropenyldiacetylene * Pentaprismane ([5]Prismane) == References == Category:Hydrocarbons
